This paper discusses the task of information extraction from text, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP). The use of pattern matching and discourse processing techniques suggests that the paper is likely to be related to computational linguistics (cs.CL). Information retrieval (cs.IR) is also a possible sub-category, as the paper deals with the extraction of relevant information from text. The use of machine learning techniques for information extraction could also place the paper in the sub-categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), or neural networks (cs.NE).
